	<Title>
		Botox injections: Can they relieve arthritis pain?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		It&apos;s unclear whether Botox injections can help arthritis pain, but early studies are promising.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can Botox injections relieve arthritis pain?
	</Question>
